Class BaseObject

  • java.lang.Object
    • Objects.BaseObject
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    BaseJSONObject, BaseScenario, House

    public abstract class BaseObject
extends java.lang.Object
    A base abstract object class to be used by other objects, this will implement base methods that should be implemented by other game objects.
